## SCORING: CORRECTNESS/DETERMINISM (co-owned with QA)

Signals (count only for patterns present, exclude generated code):

**+1 each**: single-responsibility component, typed boundaries, appropriate state level, follows dominant fetching pattern, follows naming convention, no circular deps, shared types used.

**-1 each**: `any` at boundary, mixed responsibilities (3+), pattern deviation, circular dep, redundant state, dead export.

```
Report: Correctness (ARCH): [score] ([pos]/[total]) | Δ: [+N/-N] | Evidence: [BL-IDs]
```

